{"tid":319255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔生就最好？】籲唔生仔救地球 瑞典研究語出驚人","createTime":"2017-07-12T15:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T18:21:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d45d473ebd42d85c8d278f9adf8c4ed1afd22812","tid":319255,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/235705_0e74ba944bd4682c25b7c9d3f7aa32f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F235705_0e74ba944bd4682c25b7c9d3f7aa32f2.png&h=ae55cf61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回收廢物、轉用慳電膽等是不少人常用的環保措施，但瑞典一項研究發現，要大幅減少碳排放保護環境，最「有效」的方法就是不生小朋友，有團體就鼓勵節育，認為「兩個就夠晒數」。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典隆德大學（Lund University）研究指，住在發達國家的人如果不生小朋友的話，平均每年可額外減少58.6噸碳排放，比任何節約措施帶來的影響更大，但研究發現西方國家雖然會鼓勵民眾回收廢物保護環境，卻沒有一個提倡節育。<br />\n研究作者懷恩斯（Seth Wynes）提出另外3大節約方法有助大幅減少碳排放，就是少吃肉類、棄用私家車以及少搭飛機，認為以上幾種方法再加上鼓勵組織小型家庭，比目前推廣的節約策略效果更顯著。<br />\n例如棄用私家車每人每年可減少排放2.4噸二氧化碳，而少吃肉多吃菜則可減少排放0.8噸二氧化碳。這份研究刊登在《環境研究快報》（Environmental Research Letters），懷恩斯稱只要說服到一個美國家庭少生一個小朋友，效果就等同說服684名本來不肯做回收的青少年，於下半輩子堅持廢物回收。<br />\n英國慈善組織「理想人口信託」（Optimum Population Trust）關注人口增長對自然環境的影響，該會一直提倡控制人口，並促請家長「兩個已經夠晒數」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170712/56944682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170712%2F56944682&d=GKMjGILKcLxoFPmyzF3RFOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=33c691bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170712%2F56944682&h=d195906f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170712/56944682</a>"},{"pid":"6fbf8aec6f8d3333c3f12d501f98bc449051fb44","tid":319255,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5eb0aae591bae26405915e83f8dbc8b733bb8f","tid":319255,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c3bc087609cd76e1f09fba3ab925307d8640ce","tid":319255,"uid":45213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"殺鳩支那同印度佬好過"},{"pid":"7a8dcc7dd0dcfbc54f775e7836dab5189cd2c45e","tid":319255,"uid":118120,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:47:26.000Z","msg":"劣幣驅逐良幣....愈係冇文化果d 就係咁生<br />\n有文化果d 就唔想生"},{"pid":"e6c0aa45bdada9ab2da35f05bf3deb0b5a7a7fff","tid":319255,"uid":24139,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:48:46.000Z","msg":"不如試下說服班非洲人、回人、印度同支那人嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e97695159290d03d21df8c277e6673f569777d","tid":319255,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劣幣驅逐良幣....愈係冇文化果d 就係咁生<br />\n有文化果d 就唔想生</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n伊斯蘭,中國,印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6ff9c68196fff91068a8781cf08af519024529","tid":319255,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"白人唔生 支那人印度人回教muslim同你生到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲早地球第六次生物滅絕就係因為佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6252f02b27603c69fe9ee02b90f367ddf422bf52","tid":319255,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e65f68b9a2d721328f5c7d42749db0c9236edd","tid":319255,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi